5. Accessibility Considerations
What images are you going to need alt text?
All of the images used. The description would have to relate to the image's function on the webpage.
How will you structure your headings?
H1 for the title of the page. H2 for main section headings and H3 for subsections if any.
Will you use color combinations that meet contrast guidelines?
Yes.

